text: Rocio Parrado Guarnizo (born 29 November 1982) is a Colombian professional racing cyclist. She rides for the Itau Shimano Ladies Power Team. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
